          <h1 class="text-center display-3" id="title">Ho Chi Minh (1890-1969):</h1>
          <p class="text-center h3">Major Events in the Life of a Revolutionary Leader</p>
        </header>
    </div>
    <div id="img-div" class="col-12 col-md-10 offset-md-1 img-container">
